headline: JACK HENRY & ASSOCIATES ANNOUNCES REGULAR QUARTERLY DIVIDEND
summary: Jack Henry & Associates, Inc. (NASDAQ: JKHY) today announced its Board of Directors declared a regular quarterly cash dividend of $.58 per share. The cash dividend on its common stock, par value $.01 per share, is payable on December 23, 2025, to stockholders of record as of December 2, 2025.
